data.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 1
data.text:
2003, Rated R, 110 min. Directed by Quentin Tarantino. Starring Uma Thurman, Lucy Liu, Vivica A. Fox, Michael Madsen, Daryl Hannah, David Carradine, Sonny Chiba, Chiaki Kuriyama, Gordon Liu, Michael Parks and Julie Dreyfus.

2103 E.M. Franklin Ave., 512/850-6127
